    Token

    Console program to calculate an expression in prefix notation.

    Operations.Pi
    Constant pi.
    Operations.Pow
    Exponentiation of two numbers.
    Operations.Sin
    Sine of a number in radians.
    Operations.Sqrt
    Square root of a number.
    Operations.Sub
    Subtraction of two numbers.
    Operations.ToDeg
    Converting from radians to degrees.
